title: Universal Obby Script (ONLY FOR OBBYS THAT ARE MADE BY PLATINUMFALLS)
content:
--[[
    @Author: Banqr/Sodium
    @Game: Any obby made by PlatinumFalls
    @Description: AutoComplete
    @Dependencies: TeleportPlayer, RobloxPlace
    ----------------READ ME----------------
    ONLY PLATINUMFALLS OBBYS
]]
local function teleportToCheckpoint(checkpointName)
    local checkpoint = game.Workspace:FindFirstChild(checkpointName)
    if checkpoint then
        game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = checkpoint.CFrame
    else
        warn("Checkpoint not found: " .. checkpointName)
    end
end


local function findHighestCheckpoint()
    local highestCheckpoint = 20
    for _, checkpoint in pairs(game.Workspace:GetChildren()) do
        if checkpoint:IsA("Model") and checkpoint.Name:match("^Checkpoint (%d+)$") then
            local checkpointNumber = tonumber(checkpoint.Name:match("^Checkpoint (%d+)$"))
            if checkpointNumber and checkpointNumber > highestCheckpoint then
                highestCheckpoint = checkpointNumber
            end
        end
    end
    return "Checkpoint " .. highestCheckpoint
end


local highestCheckpointName = findHighestCheckpoint()
teleportToCheckpoint(highestCheckpointName)
